/music/sleep-tokens-ii-speaks-out-on-honour-performing-at-black-sabbath-final-show-3835636">公开了关于在黑安息日的最后一场演出中表演的，称其为“崇敬和极大的荣誉”。</a></p><p>在其他新闻中，去年年底，Sleep Token神秘的蒙面歌手船<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/sleep-token-vessel-plays-nintendo-switch-during-massive-arena-show-3818696">在O2竞技场的演出中花了一些时间在他的Nintendo Switch Console上播放</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sleep-token-share-mysterious-new-sheet-music-online-this-is-what-it-sounds-like-3841877">Sleep Smot Stoken在线分享神秘的新乐谱 - 这听起来像是</a>在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首先出现的。</p> ;
米歇尔·特拉奇伯格（Michelle Trachtenberg）由联合主演罗西·奥唐奈（Rosie O'Donnell）记得：“我希望我能帮助” https://www.nme.com/news/tv/michelle-trachtenberg-remembered-by-co-star-rosie-odonnell-i-wish-i-wish-i-i-wish-i-could-could-could-could-heave-helped-3841854?utm _source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = michelle-trachtenberg重新记录逐行 - 巨星 - 罗西 - 奥德内尔 -  i-wish-i-wish-i-wish-i-i-i-wish-i-could-could-old-have-helpedVictoria Luxford Thu, 27 Feb 2025 11:50:31 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV News.. https://www.nme.com/?p=3841854 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Michelle Trachtenberg" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “吸血鬼杀手巴菲”演员于1月26日去世，享年39岁</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/michelle-trachtenberg-remembered-by-co-star-rosie-odonnell-i-wish-i-could-have-helped-3841854">米歇尔·特拉奇伯格（Michelle Trachtenberg）的邮报（Post Michelle Trachtenberg）记得联合主演Rosie O&#39;Donnell：“我希望我能帮助我”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Michelle Trachtenberg" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>演员和电视节目主持人罗西·奥唐奈（Rosie O&#39;Donnell）向前联合主演米歇尔·特拉奇伯格（Michelle Trachtenberg）致敬，后者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/buffy-and-gossip-girl-actor-michelle-trachtenberg-dies-aged-39-3841639">于1月26日去世，享年39岁</a>。</p><p>在紧急服务对911电话作出回应后，周三（1月26日）在她在纽约市的公寓中发现Trachtenberg在她的纽约市公寓无反应。当局说，这位女演员在现场被宣布死亡，医学检查官将决定死亡原因。</p><p>调查正在进行中，尽管目前尚无犯罪。</p><p>奥唐奈（O&#39;Donnell）在1996年家庭喜剧<em>《间谍》中与这位明星一起出现，</em> <a href="https://ew.com/rosie-o-donnell-reacts-michelle-trachtenberg-death-harriet-the-spy-costar-11687099" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>当时</em></a>Trachtenberg 11岁时制作。她过去几年挣扎。我希望我能有所帮助。” </p><figure id="attachment_3841863" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3841863" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3841863" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-HTS.jpg" alt="Michelle Trachtenberg" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-HTS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-HTS-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-HTS-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-HTS-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-HTS-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ODonnell-Trachtenberg-HTS-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3841863" class="wp-caption-text"> Rosie O&#39;Donnell和Michelle Trachtenberg在“ Harriet the Spy”的宣传镜头中。信用：派拉蒙图片/镍</figcaption></figure><p>米歇尔·特拉奇伯格（Michelle Trachtenberg）首先在儿童明星中首次引起公众关注，并在节目《<em>皮特与皮特（Pete＆Pete）的冒险经历》</em>以及1999年的<em>Inspector Gadget</em>中出现。成年后，她过渡到喜剧电影，拍摄电影<em>Eurotrip</em> ，<em>并在Zac Efron对面17</em> 。</p><p>然而，也许她最著名的角色是在00年代初期，当时她在表演夏天在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/buffy-the-vampire-slayer"><em>吸血鬼杀手巴菲（Buffy the Vampire Slayer）</em></a>中扮演黎明。这个角色是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sarah-michelle-gellar">莎拉·米歇尔·盖尔拉（Sarah Michelle Gellar）的</a>主角的妹妹，在节目的第五季中首次亮相，最终出现在66集中。</p><p>在2010年代，她在<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/gossip-girl"><em>八卦女孩</em>中描绘了乔治娜·斯帕克斯（Georgina Sparks）。</a>她的角色是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blake-lively">布雷克·莱弗利（Blake Lively）的</a>塞雷娜·范·德·伍德森（Serena Van der Woodsen）的前朋友，也是曼哈顿社交名流的策划人，她通常会发现自己与Serena和Leighton Meester的Blair Waldorf发生冲突。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGjD_tySCPK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" v