oads/2025/02/GreenManFestivalline-up-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/GreenManFestivalline-up-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/GreenManFestivalline-up-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/green-man">绿人节</a>宣布了2025年的阵容 - 请参阅海报，并在下面找到所有详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/green-man-festival-2023-review-self-esteem-devo-3485314">2023年绿人节：节日的胜利仍然是</a></strong></li></ul><p>独立音乐，科学和艺术活动将于8月14日至17日在威尔士的布雷肯信标举行。门票在去年9月的短短一小时内就售罄。</p><p>今天（2月27日），组织者推出了今年版本的“强大”法案。 2025年的头条新闻是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a> （星期四），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wet-leg">湿腿</a>（星期五），<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/underworld">黑社会</a>（星期六）和周日的共同饰演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tv-on-the-radio">电视，并在广播</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beth-gibbons">贝丝·吉本斯（Beth Gibbons）</a>上。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/perfume-genius">香水天才</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/english-teacher">英语老师</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yard-act">Yard Act</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kelly-lee-owens">Kelly Lee Owens</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/los-campesinos">Los Campesinos等人将加入他们的行列！</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fat-dog">胖狗</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mj-lenderman">MJ Lenderman</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/big-special">Big Special</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-grant">John Grant</a> 。</p><p>阵容的其他地方是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/divorce">离婚</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/warmduscher">，</a>成人DVD，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jasmine-4-t">茉莉花</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nilufer-yanya">。</a></p><p> “温暖的威尔士欢迎您的头条新闻，他们第一次首次超越了通用汽车账单！”组织者与官方阵容海报一起写道。</p><p> “当他们准备用他们的技术巫术进入我们时，我们将在月球上托管黑社会。再加上湿的腿，独立的独立二人组返回通用汽车的返回承诺将具有令人着迷的比例。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DGknZy0uruf/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C56