e"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">您的PlayStation以及3月的每月游戏：</p><p>龙腾世纪：面纱<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f409.png" alt="🐉" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><br />音色：终极<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f535.png" alt="🔵" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f4a8.png" alt="💨" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><br /> TMNT：Cowabunga系列<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f355.png" alt="🍕" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p> Full details: <a href="https://t.co/D7fCsJfqAN">https://t.co/D7fCsJfqAN</a> <a href="https://t.co/AyRuKJmcnX">pic.twitter.com/AyRuKJmcnX</a></p><p> — PlayStation (@PlayStation) <a href="https://twitter.com/PlayStation/status/1894787111619813874?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 26, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Also coming to PlayStation Plus next month is <em>Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles: The Cowabunga Collection</em> and <em>Sonic Colors: Ultimate</em> . The games will be added to the service on March 3 and players will have until March 31 to download them.</p><p> <em>Dragon Age: The Veilguard</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dragon-age-the-veilguard-reviews-bioware-3807166">launched with strong reviews</a> but according to a report by <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/ea-says-bookings-slid-on-weakness-in-soccer-dragon-age-games" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bloomberg</a> , the game failed to meet EA&#39;s sales expectations by almost 50 per cent. The same report claims <em>Dragon Age: The Veilguard</em> only sold 1.5million copies in its first three months.</p><p> However developers have explained that <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/dragon-age-the-veilguard-devs-were-expecting-some-people-to-hate-the-game-3819223">they expected a mixed reaction to <em>Dragon Age: The Veilguard</em></a> . “The reality was whatever we came out with, it was never going to match the <em>Dragon Age 4</em> in people&#39;s minds and people&#39;s imaginations,” said creative director John Epler. “It&#39;s not trying to be all things to all people. It&#39;s trying to be itself, it&#39;s trying to be the game that it wants to be. I think you&#39;re going to get those much more polarised reactions that way than if you make something that tries to be a little bit of everything.”</p><p> Earlier this year, Sony confirmed that from 2026, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/playstation-plus-will-shift-focus-to-ps5-games-after-2025-3833160">PlayStation Plus will be “shifting focus” to PS5 players.</a></p><p>在其他新闻中，华纳兄弟已经确认他们的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/wonder-woman">《神力女超人</a></em>》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/wonder-woman-game-cancelled-more-harry-potter-game-of-thrones-3841477">已经被取消，</a>以支持更多的<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/harry-potter">哈利·波特</a></em>和<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/game-of-thrones">《权力的游戏》</a></em>冠军。</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/playstation-plus-dragon-age-the-veilguard-march-games-3841832">PlayStation Plus is getting a recently-released epic next month</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
